metadata.name: Ray's of Eden
metadata.description:
A holy ritual in the waters from the Garden of Eden to evoke positive feelings by absorbing the energy of the special rays in the metaverse'
To wash away the negative feelings, to feel refreshed, and approach life in a positive way, I believe, we all have a holy ritual we indulge in.
In collaboration with Chelsea Kauai, a renowned adventure traveler , to whom 10% of proceeds are directed.
Artwork by Perspeaktiver.
